<section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#080808] border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
      <div class="md:w-1/2 relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#CC0000]/20 blur-[50px] rounded-full group-hover:bg-[#CC0000]/30 transition-all duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1415&q=80"
          alt="Proyeksi Bisnis 5 Tahun"
          class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-[#CC0000]/10 w-full border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/10 filter brightness-90 group-hover:brightness-100 transition-all duration-500"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="md:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight">
          Proyeksi <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#CC0000] to-[#ff4444] italic">Bisnis</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Dengan model bisnis auto-pilot yang sudah teruji, outlet PITCAR Service menunjukkan tren pertumbuhan eksponensial yang stabil setiap kuartalnya.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start bg-white dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="bg-[#CC0000]/10 p-4 rounded-xl mr-5 shrink-0 border border-[#CC0000]/20">
              <i class="fas fa-chart-line text-[#CC0000] text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Volume Order Konstan</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60">Sistem manajemen reservasi menjamin flow kendaraan harian padat.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start bg-white dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="bg-[#CC0000]/10 p-4 rounded-xl mr-5 shrink-0 border border-[#CC0000]/20">
              <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave text-[#CC0000] text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Omzet Bertumbuh</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60">Rata-rata lonjakan omzet cabang mencapai 25-30% YoY.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start bg-white dark:bg-[#141414] border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl hover:border-[#CC0000]/30 transition-colors duration-300">
            <div class="bg-[#CC0000]/10 p-4 rounded-xl mr-5 shrink-0 border border-[#CC0000]/20">
              <i class="fas fa-percentage text-[#CC0000] text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white text-lg uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Margin Profit High-Yield</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-white/60">Optimalisasi suplai sparepart pusat menekan HPP dan memaksimalkan margin bersih.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
